title.Name: title
title.Value: Northshore Hills Road Race - Group 8 - Race 6

description.Name: description
description.Value:
Round:  2
Cars:  Ferrari F40 vs. Mustang Mach 1
Teams:  Max-G vs. Easy Iron

The Ferrari F40 from team Max-G looked really fast in its victory today over the Mustang Mach 1 from team Easy Iron.  It seemed to get launched through the S-turns with the help of the Mustang at the start of each run which gave it a huge lead both times.  It would have most likely taken a DNF for the Mach 1 to have a chance at that point.  This win puts the F40 through to the final round where it will faceoff with the Firebird SE from team MxV.  Come back tomorrow to see who wins the last group stage of the NSH Road Race.
